OL,3,CMan arrested after 'alleged racially
OL,4,Cmotivated assault' outside mosque
OL,6,FA man has been arrested by Jersey
OL,7,Fpolice after an 'alleged racially
OL,8,Fmotivated assault' outside the
OL,9,Fisland's Islamic Centre.
OL,11,FThe alleged offence took place on
OL,12,FAquila Road, St Helier, at
OL,13,Fapproximately 2pm on Friday 6 March.
OL,15,FPolice confirmed that a 51-year-old
OL,16,Fmale has been arrested on suspicion of
OL,17,Fcommon assault and disorderly conduct
OL,18,Fin a statement, adding that it
OL,19,Finvolved two male victims.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
