FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1773072685
OL,3,CMan arrested after 'alleged racially
OL,4,Cmotivated assault' outside mosque
OL,6,FITV News has spoken to eyewitnesses at
OL,7,Fthe scene following the incident, and
OL,8,Fthere are varied accounts of what
OL,9,Fhappened.
OL,11,FSome report seeing a child being
OL,12,Fushered into the mosque for their own
OL,13,Fsafety.
OL,15,FOther residents say two separate
OL,16,Fpeople were themselves pushed by
OL,17,Fmembers of the Muslim community, but
OL,18,Fthe police have not verified that
OL,19,Fincident.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1773072685
OL,3,CMan arrested after 'alleged racially
OL,4,Cmotivated assault' outside mosque
OL,6,FPolice say that no serious injuries
OL,7,Fwere reported.
OL,9,FA statement from the force reads: "We
OL,10,Fwill not tolerate any form of hate
OL,11,Fcrime, which can have a harmful ripple
OL,12,Feffect across our Island.
OL,14,F"Our Police Community Safety Team is
OL,15,Fworking to support members of the
OL,16,FMuslim community connected to Jersey's
OL,17,FIslamic Centre."
OL,19,FDr Sarfraz Jamil, the head of Jersey's
OL,20,FMuslim Community, said the community
OL,21,Fare "concerned".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1773072685
OL,3,CMan arrested after 'alleged racially
OL,4,Cmotivated assault' outside mosque
OL,6,F"They are shaken, and they are
OL,7,Fdisappointed," Dr Jamil told ITV News.
OL,8,F"They are more worried if there is a
OL,9,Flot of intimidation, and they are now
OL,10,Fworried about their safety.
OL,12,F"Even I am concerned, what if my wife
OL,13,Fcomes to prayer all alone, will she
OL,14,Ffeel safe all alone or not?"
OL,16,F"I have been here since 1998, and I
OL,17,Fhave enjoyed the peace and the love,
OL,18,Fand I am disappointed to see this
OL,19,Fhappen and hoping it is a one-off
OL,20,Fincident."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1773072685
OL,3,CMan arrested after 'alleged racially
OL,4,Cmotivated assault' outside mosque
OL,6,FThe Chief Minister, Deputy Lyndon
OL,7,FFarnham, called the incident
OL,8,F"distressing" and "deeply concerning"
OL,9,Ffor members of the Muslim community.
OL,11,FIn a statement, he said: "I am
OL,12,Freassured that the police responded
OL,13,Fswiftly, that one individual has been
OL,14,Farrested, and that further enquiries
OL,15,Fare ongoing.
OL,17,F"It is important that this matter is
OL,18,Finvestigated fully, and I know the
OL,19,Fpolice are treating it with the
OL,20,Fseriousness it deserves.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1773072685
OL,3,CMan arrested after 'alleged racially
OL,4,Cmotivated assault' outside mosque
OL,6,F"The Muslim community in Jersey has my
OL,7,Ffull support."
OL,9,FOther faith groups in the island have
OL,10,Fcome out to show their support for the
OL,11,FMuslim community.
OL,13,FJersey's Jewish Congregation has
OL,14,Freleased a statement, condemning all
OL,15,Facts of racially-motivated violence.
OL,17,FThey said, "We are horrified that this
OL,18,Fhas happened on our peaceful island."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38507
