CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1773072685
OL,3,CMan arrested after 'alleged racially
OL,4,Cmotivated assault' outside mosque
OL,6,F"All our prayers and thoughts are with
OL,7,Fthe Muslim Community, and we will say
OL,8,Fa special prayer for healing for the
OL,9,Fvictim at our service on Saturday
OL,10,Fmorning."
OL,12,FPolice investigations remain ongoing.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/7
